{"tid":1517500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好奇怪 次次都係臨作戰時就有其他意見","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:46.000Z","uid":11374,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"02b824202b6ca6cc69921abd94142906893476ca","tid":1517500,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"就黎開學 大家期待已久 講到明 唔同狗仔狗女玩<br />\n喂大佬 我冇叫你欺凌佢<br />\n只係大家都有選擇朋友既自由<br />\n有身同惑受既就知 比全部人當隱形係最撚慘<br />\n分組冇人同佢分<br />\n食飯冇人同佢食<br />\n小息個個同學都圍埋傾計吹水 狗仔就要諗方法喱埋 唔想見人<br />\n<br />\n事情發生左就黎3個月 並沒有中立既存在<br />\n如果狗仔同狗老豆老母係意見分歧 站在我地既一方 <br />\n有出黎表達意見既 立埸鮮明<br />\n我個人認為 佢係有良知既人 大家依然可以同有良知既朋友交往<br />\n<br />\n我簡男/女朋友都要政治立埸一樣啦, 朋友WHY NOT<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係突然有大量POST又話要感化 又話要導狗仔/女向善<br />\n睇得出D狗真係好撚驚佢地仔/女既開學日<br />\n你班狗打人仔女,射爆人眼, 性欺凌 果陣 唔諗下 大家都係香港人 大家都有老豆老母生?<br />\n<br />\n唔好又突然做都未做 又話有其他IDEA啦<br />\n試左個成效先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2bf13bbc68afc74a652d06c12ad1a87d0c4bf1ab","tid":1517500,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8iq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=262bcef6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8iq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=4f2b9b5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=